title: Jeanines
text:
Jeanines are an American indie pop band from New York City. The duo is currently signed to Slumberland Records.


== History ==
Jeanines began in the 2010s with singer Alicia Hyman and bassist/drummer Jed Smith. In 2019, Jeanines released their debut self-titled album. In 2022, the duo followed up their debut with their second full-length album titled Don't Wait for a Sign. The album received positive reviews.
